            "title": "ssh-nopasswd",
            "date_published": "2023-01-07T01:19:47.000Z",
            "content_html": "<ol>\n<li>ssh 客户端端执行 ssh-keygen  生成公钥和私钥到~/.ssh\n<blockquote>\n<p>具体文件为 ~/.ssh/id_rsa(私钥)  ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub（公钥）</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>ssh-copy-id -i ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub <a href=\"mailto:root@192.168.235.22\">root@192.168.235.22</a> 上传公钥到ssh服务器，指定服务器ip和ssh用户名</li>\n<li>ssh <a href=\"mailto:root@192.168.235.22\">root@192.168.235.22</a> 执行免密登陆</li>\n</ol>\n",
            "tags": [
                "tool",
                "ssh"
            ]
        }
    ]
